sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Claude
    participant HM as Hooks Manager
    participant CI as Context Injection Hook
    participant CMD as Command
    participant FS as Filesystem

    U->>C: /arckit:command
    C->>HM: UserPromptSubmit event
    HM->>CI: Execute hook
    CI->>FS: Scan projects/ (Node.js)
    CI->>FS: Read artifacts (batch)
    CI->>FS: Extract metadata
    CI->>CI: Build structured tables
    CI->>HM: additionalContext payload
    HM->>C: Inject context
    C->>CMD: Execute with pre-loaded data
    Note over C,CMD: Command sees tables,<br/>skips I/O steps
    CMD->>C: Generate output
    C->>U: Result (0 Read calls)
